@div sa-gida A

$ (unknown no. of lines missing)
A.1. šul {d}[utu ... im]-ma-an-ri
#lem: šul[youth]; Utu[1]DN; X; ri[impose]
#etcsl: line-id=A.1

A.2. ur₅-ra-aš-ta X [...] mu#-e-tum₃-tum₃
#lem: Uraš[1]DN; X; X; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

A.3. še-er-zid piriŋ gal# [...] X ur#-saŋ <an>-šag₄ kug-ta e₃!(DU)-a
#lem: šerzid[radiance]; piriŋ[lion]; gal[big]; X; X; ursaŋ[warrior]; anšag[the interior of heaven]; kug[pure]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

A.4. ud me-lem₄-ni kalam-ma bi₂-dul₄ ni₂ gal mu-da-ri
#lem: ud[storm]; melim[frightening splendor]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; dul[cover]; ni[fear]; gal[big]; ri[impose]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

A.5. {d}utu lugal niŋ₂-si-sa₂ a zid-de₃-eš₂ tum₂-ma
#lem: Utu[1]DN; lugal[king]; niŋsisa[justice]; a[water]; zid[right]; tum[suitable]
#etcsl: line-id=A.5

A.6. šen-na dalla mu-na-ni-in-e₃ sipad zid šul-gi-ke₄
#lem: šen[battle]; dalla[(to be) bright]; e[leave]; sipad[shepherd]; zid[right]; Šulgir[1]RN
#etcsl: line-id=A.6

A.7. am gal an kug-ta šul {d}utu izi-ŋar-gin₇ ŋa₂-ŋa₂ ud kalam-ma igi-ŋal₂
#lem: am[wild bull]; gal[big]; an[sky]; kug[pure]; šul[youth]; Utu[1]DN; iziŋar[torch]; ŋar[put]; ud[storm]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; igiŋal[wise]
#etcsl: line-id=A.7

A.8. [kur]-kur-ra me-lem₄ ur₅-ra-aš
#lem: kur[mountain(s)]; melim[frightening splendor]; Uraš[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=A.8

A.9. diŋir si sa₂ <{d}>a-nun-ke₄-ne ušumgal# kug sud-sud
#lem: diŋir[deity]; si[horn]; sa[equal]; Anunak[1]DN; ušumgal[great dragon]; kug[purify]; sud[distant]
#etcsl: line-id=A.9

A.10. dumu-saŋ {d}suen-ne₂ mi₂ dug₄-ga en dug₄-ga tud-da
